column1: Well, be careful on your way back.
See ya, [1B]S1. It was a real blast.

Drop us a line whenever you're back. No matter
what we're doing, we'll drop it to meet you.
We'll be waiting to hear from you.

Are you gonna be back for winter break?
You know you could come back sooner,
right?

The attic's all yours whenever you like—it'll only
cost you a few hours behind the counter.

Lady Ann! While it pains me to leave you,
I must keep watch over [1B]S1...

See you later, Mona-chan! Listen to your
owner, okay?
No, HE listens to ME! And I'm not a pet!

Keep an eye on these two for us, okay,
Sophia?
I have a present for Sophia!

Indeed! I didn't get a chance to give it to you
yesterday—

Oh! One moment, Futaba—there's a message
from Ichinose!

I admit I'm curious as well... Are any of you too
busy to join us?
Not at all—in fact, this seems right.
Yes, one last little farewell trip together.
